title: Canon Digital Camera Solution Disk ver 31.0
description:
Unfortunately Canon insists that you have the actual cd in order to upgrade their software - so for those who have lost the cd that came with their Canon or it's too damaged, here you go.

Canon Digital Camera Solution Disk ver 31.0 provided with the Canon EOS 40D

Contains Canon Utilities:

For Mac:
Image Browser 6.0
Photo Stitch 3.2
EOS Utility 1.1

For Windows:
ZoombBrowser EX 6.0
PhotoStitch 3.1
Camera TWAIN driver 6.8
EOS Utility 1.1a

Once you have the cd, you can grab the necessary updates from Canon at http://canon.ca/english/index-softwaredownload.aspg
